wt.templateutil.components

Class CheckBoxCellComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • wt.templateutil.components.HTMLComponent
      • wt.templateutil.components.HTMLTableCellComponent
        • wt.templateutil.components.DisableableCheckBoxCellComponent
          • wt.templateutil.components.CheckBoxCellComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Deprecated.

    public class CheckBoxCellComponent
extends DisableableCheckBoxCellComponent
implements java.io.Serializable
    This component can be used with CheckBoxTableColumn to display a checkbox in a table cell which can not be disabled.

    Deprecation Notice: This class is still valid for this release, however this serves as advance notice that it will be removed in the future. All user interfaces built using the Windchill HTML Template Processing client architecture will be rewritten using a different framework in an upcoming release.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
